e="button" class="button btn-auth small no-border">Log in</button><div class="language-selector"><div class=" css-b62m3t-container" id="languageSelector"><span id="react-select-3-live-region" class="css-7pg0cj-a11yText"></span><span aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="false" aria-relevant="additions text" role="log" class="css-7pg0cj-a11yText"></span><div class=" css-v1nj60-control"><div class=" css-hlgwow"><div class=" css-1hyilnf-singleValue">English</div><input id="react-select-3-input" tabindex="0" inputmode="none" aria-autocomplete="list" aria-expanded="false" aria-haspopup="true" role="combobox" aria-activedescendant="" aria-readonly="true" class="css-1hac4vs-dummyInput" value=""></div><div class=" css-1jr0ejv"><span class=" css-1uei4ir-indicatorSeparator"></span><div class=" css-1xc3v61-indicatorContainer" aria-hidden="true"><svg height="20" width="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="css-8mmkcg"><path d="M4.516 7.548c0.436-0.446 1.043-0.481 1.576 0l3.908 3.747 3.908-3.747c0.533-0.481 1.141-0.446 1.574 0 0.436 0.445 0.408 1.197 0 1.615-0.406 0.418-4.695 4.502-4.695 4.502-0.217 0.223-0.502 0.335-0.787 0.335s-0.57-0.112-0.789-0.335c0 0-4.287-4.084-4.695-4.502s-0.436-1.17 0-1.615z"></path></svg></div></div></div><input name="language" type="hidden" value="en"></div></div><div><div class="side-panel"><nav><ul><li><a class="is-active" href="/en/assets/logos">Logos</a></li></ul></nav></div><div class="form-buttons"><button type="button" class="button small">Account Request</button></div></div></div><div id="main" class="transition-in"><div class="frame"><div class="side-panel"><nav><ul><li><a class="is-active" href="/en/assets/logos">Logos</a></li></ul></nav></div><div id="content"><article id="page-logos"><section class="page-header"><hr><h3 lang="en">The N Symbol and <span class="nf">Company</span> Wordmark</h3><button type="button" class="button download">DOWNLOAD</button></section><section id="section-n-symbol" class="section"><hr><div class="row section-header"><div class="half"><h4>N Symbol</h4></div><div class="half"><div class="text"><p>In high-awareness markets, we lead with the N Symbol. There is power in owning a letter of the alphabet: it’s universal and instantly identifiable as shorthand for our brand. However, without <span class="nf">Company</span> Red, the N Symbol might not read as <span class="nf">Company</span>, which is why it <strong>always appears in its signature color</strong>.</p></div></div></div><div class="row items"><div class="full"><img src="//images.ctfassets.net/y2ske730sjqp/5QQ9SVIdc1tmkqrtFnG9U1/de758bba0f65dcc1c6bc1f31f161003d/BrandAssets_Logos_02-NSymbol.jpg?w=940" class="" alt="BrandAssets Logos  NSymbol"></div></div></section><section id="section-wordmark" class="section"><hr><div class="row section-header"><div class="half"><h4>Wordmark</h4></div><div class="half"><div class="text"><p>The Wordmark remains an essential identifier of our brand. While our goal is to lead with the N Symbol, we enlist the Wordmark to ensure brand recognition in low-awareness markets or when production limits the use of color.</p></div></div></div><div class="row items"><div class="full"><img src="//images.ctfassets.net/y2ske730sjqp/1aONibCke6niZhgPxuiilC/2c401b05a07288746ddf3bd3943fbc76/BrandAssets_Logos_01-Wordmark.jpg?w=940" class="" alt="BrandAssets Logos  Wordmark"></div></div></section><section id="section-color" class="section color-assets"><hr><div class="row section-header"><div class="half"><h4>Color</h4></div><div class="half"><div class="text"><p>The Symbol should appear in our brand standard Red and our Symbol Dark Red. The Wordmark should appear in our brand standard Red, except when limited by production (see Special-use Wordmarks below).</p></div></div></div><div class="row items"><div class="third"><img src="//images.ctfassets.net/y2ske730sjqp/4aEQ1zAUZF5pLSDtfviWjb/ba04f8d5bd01428f6e3803cc6effaf30/Company_N.png?w=300" class="" alt="Company N"></div><div class="swatch"><div class="color-circle" style="background-color: rgb(229, 9, 20);"></div><div class="color-details"><p><strong>Company Red</strong></p><ul><li><strong>RGB</strong> 229 9 20</li><li><strong>HEX</strong> E50914</li><li><strong>CMYK</strong> 0 96 93 2</li><li><strong>PMS</strong> 1795 C</li></ul></div></div><div class="swatch"><div class="color-circle" style="background-color: rgb(178, 7, 16);"></div><div class="color-details"><p><strong>Symbol Dark Red</strong></p><ul><li><strong>RGB</strong> 178 7 16</li><li><strong>HEX</strong> B20710</li><li><strong>CMYK</strong> 18 100 100 10</li><li><strong>PMS</strong> 7627 C</li></ul></div></div></div></section><section id="subsection-color-assets-2" class="subsection no-divider color-assets"><hr><div class="row section-header no-text"></div><div class="row items"><div class="half"><img src="//images.ctfassets.net/y2ske730sjqp/821Wg4N9hJD8vs5FBcCGg/9eaf66123397cc61be14e40174123c40/Vector__3_.svg?w=460" class="" alt="Vector   "></div><div class="swatch"><div class="color-circle" style="background-color: rgb(229, 9, 20);"></div><div class="color-details"><p><strong>Company Red</strong></p><ul><li><strong>RGB</strong> 229 9 20</li><li><strong>HEX</strong> E50914</li><li><strong>CMYK</strong> 0 96 93 2</li><li><strong>PMS</strong> 1795 C</li></ul></div></div></div></section><section id="section-clearspace" class="section"><hr><div class="row section-header"><div class="half"><h4>Clearspace</h4></div><div class="half"><div class="text"><p>We’re a confident brand. We never crowd our logos and always give them room to breathe and stand out. The clear space around the N Symbol is the width of one leg of the N. The clear space around the Wordmark is the width of the T.</p></div></div></div><div class="row items"><div class="half"><img src="//images.ctfassets.net/y2ske730sjqp/7K8Pu8no6ETS4y2LfwwOkk/cad432ea54720510cc71560f6bc78c35/BrandAssets_Logos_03-ClearSpace_01.jpg?w=460" class="" alt="BrandAssets Logos  ClearSpace "></div><div class="half"><img src="//images.ctfassets.net/y2ske730sjqp/wXQuYIpMOFBkAKGgTJmBu/1708a448bbd1c0b48e7a44a6485788c4/BrandAssets_Logos_03-ClearSpace_02.jpg?w=460" class="" alt="BrandAssets Logos  ClearSpace "></div></div></section><section id="section-in-context" class="section"><hr><div class="row section-header"><div class="half"><h4>In Context</h4></div><div class="half"><div class="text"><p>Our logos commonly appear on solid colors, Textures, and content. Proper contrast ensures logo readability.</p></div></div></div><div class="row items"><div class="half"><div class="animation"><div class="animation-container border"><img src="//images.ctfassets.net/y2ske730sjqp/3F1XDmp66F76BWsWIIwOPM/8267247baa32bbd32162ff893396c992/Logos-In-Context-Stream.jpg" data-frames="//images.ctfassets.net/y2ske730sjqp/5kBt27I3A5gIXvF4uTQkbk/8ef2a2efb969d65c3b47ba47344f88ed/Logos-In-Context-Purple-background.jpg,//images.ctfassets.net/y2ske730sjqp/3F1XDmp66F76BWsWIIwOPM/8267247baa32bbd32162ff893396c992/Logos-In-Context-Stream.jpg,//images.ctfassets.net/y2ske730sjqp/feMIPEslgdOIkSoME4Inj/4046fa1973f04316ad0093a933891aa0/Logos-In-Context-Map.jpg" data-current="1" class="section-image animated" alt=""><div class="overlay"></div></div></div></div><div class="half"><div class="animation"><div class="animation-container border"><img src="//images.ctfassets.net/y2ske730sjqp/3F1XDmp66F76BWsWIIwOPM/8267247baa32bbd32162ff893396c992/Logos-In-Context-Stream.jpg" data-frames="//images.ctfassets.net/y2ske730sjqp/5kBt27I3A5gIXvF4uTQkbk/8ef2a2efb969d65c3b47ba47344f88ed/Logos-In-Context-Purple-background.jpg,//images.ctfassets.net/y2ske730sjqp/3F1XDmp66F76BWsWIIwOPM/8267247baa32bbd32162ff893396c992/Logos-In-Context-Stream.jpg,//images.ctfassets.net/y2ske730sjqp/feMIPEslgdOIkSoME4Inj/4046fa1973f04316ad0093a933891aa0/Logos-In-Context-Map.jpg" data-current="1" class="section-image animated" alt=""><div class="overlay"></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-readability" class="section"><hr><div class="row section-header"><div class="half"><h4>Readability</h4></div><div class="half"><div class="text"><p>When placing a logo on a background, aim for a contrast ratio of 2.25:1 or higher to ensure readability. If the contrast is too low, adjust the background or choose a different one. Check color contrast <strong><a href="https://webaim.org/resources/contrastchecker/" target="_blank">here</a></strong>.</p></div></div></div><div class="row items"><div class="quarter"><div class="animation" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div class="animation-container border"><img src="//images.ctfassets.net/y2ske730sjqp/6bhPChRFLRxc17sR8jgKbe/6fa1c6e6f37acdc97ff635cf16ba6fb3/Logos-Readability-Company-logo.png" data-frames="//images.ctfassets.net/y2ske730sjqp/2GxOK8ErCUIO3JmOIKftuc/6eff5ac8732196f68b7d0e2d2af81b8c/Logos-Readability-N-Symbol.png,//images.ctfassets.net/y2ske730sjqp/6bhPChRFLRxc17sR8jgKbe/6fa1c6e6f37acdc97ff635cf16ba6fb3/Logos-Readability-Company-logo.png" data-current="1" class="section-image animated" alt="0% Black  
